<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-10-0421 </DOCNO><TEXT>After some basic notes on federalism, liberalism and market-economicalpolicies, the problems of competences of government instances concerningthe involvement in energy policy is dealt with. As for energy policy,the author emphasizes three public values to justify government's intervention:ensuring national supply; the dependence of some sorts of energy on theway of their transmission, and protection of the environment.</TEXT></DOC>